Localization.Name: Snaggle Stick (Smoke Daddy)
Localization.Description:
NDR: 14
Effects: Hypertrophic, Dehydrating

Snag one of these premium protein sticks and experience the ultimate in "real meat" snacking. Smoke Daddy Snaggle sticks feature an extra blast of intense smoky flavor that delivers satisfaction.
